div.p: No. 1740, VPRS 1164 register of inwards correspondence, vol. 10, VA 672 Premier's Office, Public Record Office, Victoria.
THIS FILE IS A DUPLICATE RECORD

of M to A. McLean, 17 June 1891, forwarded from the Chief Secretary's office to the Premier's office.
M to A. McLean, 17 June 1891 (in this edition as 91-06-17a).
It was previously treated as a letter from M to the Premier, James Munro.
